Package: autolabel
Title: Apply Variable and Value Labels to Register Data
Version: 3.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeffrey", "Clark", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jeffrey@registream.org"),
    person("Jie", "Wen", role = "aut",
           email = "jie@registream.org"))
Description: Applies curated variable and value labels from the
    RegiStream metadata catalog to data frames of administrative
    register data. Labels are stored as column attributes via the
    'haven' labelled convention so they round-trip through Stata DTA
    files and integrate cleanly with tidyverse and base R workflows.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    registream (>= 3.0.0),
    haven
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Encoding: UTF-8
Config/testthat/edition: 3
